OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPC Andrew Harper's widow   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwins bid to change law     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A campaign by PC Andrew Harper's widow 
OL,6, to give mandatory life sentences to the
OL,7, killers of emergency service workers   
OL,8, has been backed by the government.     
OL,10,FNewly-married PC Harper was 28 when he 
OL,11,Fwas dragged to his death by a getaway  
OL,12,Fcar in August 2019. Three teenagers    
OL,13,Fwere jailed for manslaughter.          
OL,15,FThe Ministry of Justice said it would  
OL,16,Faim to pass Harper's Law in England and
OL,17,FWales "as soon as possible".           
OL,19,FLissie Harper said she was delighted   
OL,20,Fand her late husband would be proud.   
